  "detailed_description": "Fight your alongside or against your friends with PvP and PvE Roguelike game modes! Choose from eight unique classes, Pyromancer, Ice Magus, Grave Warden, Druid, Trapper, Pirate Captain, Assassin, and Paladin, each with its own distinct playstyle and abilities. Pick 4 abilities from each class's selection, each containing at least 5 or more options to pick from! Head into the PvE roguelike arena to challenge deadly foes and gain numerous upgrades to create a distinct build! In PvP, suit your preferred combat style with 12 perks to be a ranger, a mini mage, and much more. Engage in up to 4v4 battles across multiple game modes and maps with your friends and prove you are the craziest mage of them all. <br><br><strong>Fight against powerful enemies!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.poster.avif?t=1746024249\" width=554 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.webm?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.mp4?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Or against your friends</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/3733949d9cc25bcbb49061c6366620df.poster.avif?t=1746024249\" width=554 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/3733949d9cc25bcbb49061c6366620df.webm?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/3733949d9cc25bcbb49061c6366620df.mp4?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Customize your character to suit your playstyle!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/c474109a6138b19a0ab89ac174151829.poster.avif?t=1746024249\" width=554 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/c474109a6138b19a0ab89ac174151829.webm?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/c474109a6138b19a0ab89ac174151829.mp4?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Fight your alongside or against your friends with PvP and PvE Roguelike game modes! Choose from eight unique classes, Pyromancer, Ice Magus, Grave Warden, Druid, Trapper, Pirate Captain, Assassin, and Paladin, each with its own distinct playstyle and abilities. Pick 4 abilities from each class's selection, each containing at least 5 or more options to pick from! Head into the PvE roguelike arena to challenge deadly foes and gain numerous upgrades to create a distinct build! In PvP, suit your preferred combat style with 12 perks to be a ranger, a mini mage, and much more. Engage in up to 4v4 battles across multiple game modes and maps with your friends and prove you are the craziest mage of them all. <br><br><strong>Fight against powerful enemies!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.poster.avif?t=1746024249\" width=554 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.webm?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/00928cabab4a1668a4dfecea5949cc6b.mp4?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Or against your friends</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/3733949d9cc25bcbb49061c6366620df.poster.avif?t=1746024249\" width=554 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/3733949d9cc25bcbb49061c6366620df.webm?t=1746024249\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2433320/extras/373394